## Endpoints

### Vuelos

- GET /flights/
- POST /flights/
- DELETE /flights/{code}?mode=ELIMINAR|CANCELAR
- GET /flights/metrics
- GET /flights/economics
- GET /flights/audit
- GET /flights/compare
- POST /flights/stress-mode
- POST /flights/rebalance-global

### Cola de inserciones

- POST /flights/queue
- GET /flights/queue
- POST /flights/queue/process

### Versionado

- POST /versions/save
- GET /versions/
- POST /versions/restore/{name}
- DELETE /versions/{name}

### Carga, exportacion y undo

- POST /trees/load-file
- GET /trees/export/topology
- GET /trees/export/insertion
- POST /trees/export/topology-file
- POST /trees/export/insertion-file
- POST /trees/undo

## Ejecucion local de la API

1. cd C:/Desktop/Proyect-data-structures
2. ./.venv/Scripts/Activate.ps1
3. uvicorn app:app --reload
4. Abrir http://127.0.0.1:8000/docs

## Pruebas

Ejecutar pruebas unitarias:

1. cd C:/Desktop/Proyect-data-structures
2. ./.venv/Scripts/Activate.ps1
3. python -m unittest discover -s tests -p "test\_\*.py"
